---
title: "Is Coffee Supply More Concentrated Than the Catalog Suggests?"
date: "2026-04-22"
description: "The public green coffee shelf looks diverse. The fresh flow of new listings is much narrower, more concentrated by origin, and more relevant to buyers who actually care about freshness."
tags: ["coffee", "market-intelligence", "supply-chain", "data"]
